<l>kalaṅkātu kaṇṭa viṉaikkaṭ ṭuḷaṅkātu </l>
<l>tūkkaṅ kaṭintu ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>An act that has been firmly resolved on must be as firmly carried out without delay.</l>
